(Karen Olkowski )

<li>
<b>Jan 31 - <a href="traildetail.asp?Id=141">Afterglow Lake Resort</a> (Phelps):</b><br>
Conditions: As good as it gets.<br>Great skiing on the best groomed trails in the Midwest.<br>
(Bob Faherty)

<li>
<b>Jan 31 - <a href="traildetail.asp?Id=141">Afterglow Lake Resort</a> (Phelps):</b><br>
